WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Discover how reef food chains work!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Energy flows from small plankton to big fish in organised chains.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Each creature has an important role in the reef ecosystem.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
We can use numbers to count and track these relationships.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Mathematics helps us understand nature's amazing connections!